uiEntry.title: button_advice
uiEntry.tooltip: Help||This will take you to the in-game encyclopaedia.

uiEntry.title: time_label
uiEntry.tooltip: When this timer runs out, the battle will be fought according to the default setting. || The default setting is the button that is highlighted.

uiEntry.title: header_bar_title_center
uiEntry.tooltip: Once you have captured a settlement, you need to decide what to do with it.||Mouse over the sections below for more details.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Looting will damage all buildings within the castle town and will have a negative effect on the daimyo's honour.

uiEntry.title: loot_text_button
uiEntry.tooltip: Looting a settlement will provide a lot of money in the short term, but it will damage more buildings and public order will be worse, making it harder to keep control of the settlement.
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("settlement_captured"))
function EmbeddedOnMouseLClickUp() parent :LuaCall("LootSettlement") end

uiEntry.title: button_txt
uiEntry.tooltip: Looting will provide more money than peaceful occupation, but may also damage buildings and negatively affect public order in the province.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Peaceful occupation will result in minor damage to military buildings within the castle town.

uiEntry.title: occupy_text_button
uiEntry.tooltip: Peaceful occupation gives less money than looting, but fewer buildings will be damaged and public order will be better, making it easier to keep control of the settlement and develop it.
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("settlement_captured"))
function EmbeddedOnMouseLClickUp() parent :LuaCall("OccupySettlement") end

uiEntry.title: button_txt
uiEntry.tooltip: Peaceful occupation gives less money than looting, but fewer buildings will be damaged and public order will be better, making it easier to keep control of the settlement and develop it.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: In making this clan a vassal, they will receive your protection in return for a regular tribute and free reign over their territory.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: As a mark of respect for their new masters, the vassal will provide your clan with one military unit.

uiEntry.title: vassal_text_button
uiEntry.tooltip: If this was the last settlement of this clan, you can give them a stay of execution by making them a vassal clan.||This means they receive protection from you in return for a regular payment and full access to their lands.
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("settlement_captured"))
function EmbeddedOnMouseLClickUp() parent :LuaCall("LiberateSettlement") end

uiEntry.title: button_txt
uiEntry.tooltip: If this was the last settlement of this clan, you can give them a stay of execution by making them a vassal clan.||This means they receive protection from you in return for a regular payment and full access to their lands.
